item.title: Compiling Problem
item.dc:creator: @bbl111 bbl111
item.description:
@bbl111 wrote:

Right click your compiler and click edit. There should be something like

C:/Program Files/Jdk6_u7/bin/javac
and just change the
Jdk6_u7
to your current version of java.
